Description: Provides a comprehensive suite of estimation tools for meanimiles, 
    a general class of (risk) functionals. This package includes nonparametric 
    estimators for univariate meanimile evaluation, copula-based estimation 
    for portfolio risk aggregation (full parametric, semiparametric, and nonparametric),
    and novel estimators for meanimiles in regression settings. 
    Following the articles D. Debrauwer, I. Gijbels, and K. Herrmann (2025)
    <doi:10.1214/25-EJS2391>, D. Debrauwer and I. Gijbels (2026)
    <doi:10.1007/s00184-026-01022-9>.
